keywords.term: T. Crystallization and Preliminary X-ray Diffraction Studies of Perchloric Acid Soluble Protein (PSP) from Rat Liver. Acta Cryst D.

div.p: We collected an excellent native dataset on percloric acid soluble protein (PSP) to 1.8 A resolution in cryo-cooling conditions. The crystals belong to cubic space group P2,3 with cell dimensions a=b=c=89.743 A. The collected data are 97.9 % complete (96.6% in the last shell from 1.83 -1.80 A). 74050 reflections were collected, and merged to 22151 unique reflections with the overall Rmerge of 0.032 (0.277 in the last resolution shell). The structure solution is in progress.
